description: ORHub, Inc. provides surgical software focusing on real-time surgical data analytics. The company's suite of products serves the needs of the health care industry, hospitals, patients, the government, and medical device vendors. The company provides a cloud-based software solution that captures information before, during, and after surgery. Its software applications allow hospitals and medical device vendors to utilize Web-enabled device to create an anatomical graphic depiction during surgery. The company is based in Phoenix, Arizona.
